  "texts": [
    "BPM: the best-performing methods for the 'ontology-based PFP benchmark' in that original publication.",
    "The performances were assessed based on F max, and the performances of AnnoPRO, BPM, DeepGOPlus, and PFmulDL were highlighted in light red, orange, light green, and light blue, respectively.",
    "Each of those quadrangular-stars represented the best-performing model under a particular GO category and GO class.",
    "(a) Biological Process; (b) Molecular Function; and (c) Cellular Component.",
    "As illustrated, the AnnoPRO demonstrated the best performances in the vast majority (17 out of 18) of the studied GO categories Table 22A comparison among those performances of AnnoPRO and two state-of-the-art methods (DeepGOPlus and PFmulDL) on predicting two groups of 'Independent Testing' data (SameSP and DiffSP)SameSP had 1,859 proteins from 17 species covered by 'Training' and 'Validation' datasets of this study; DiffSP included 3,764 proteins from the remaining 997 species unique in 'Independent Testing' data of this study."
